==生物上的功能==
在動物組織中，BCKDC催化不可逆步驟<ref>{{cite journal | author = Yeaman SJ | title =The 2-oxo acid dehydrogenase complexes: recent advances. | journal = Biochem J.| volume = 257| issue = 3| pages = 625–632| year = 1989 | pmid = 2649080}}</ref> ，分解代謝的支鏈氨基酸，即L-[[異白胺酸|異白胺酸]]，L-[[纈氨酸|纈氨酸]]和L-[[白胺酸|白胺酸]]及其衍生物（分別是L-α-酮-β-甲基戊酸酯，[[α-酮異戊酸|α-酮異戊酸]]和α-酮異己酸鹽）。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Broquist HP, Trupin JS. | title = Amino Acid Metabolism | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_annual-review-of-biochemistry_1966_35/page/231 | journal = Annual Review of Biochemistry| volume = 35| pages = 231–247| year = 1966 | doi = 10.1146/annurev.bi.35.070166.001311}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Harris RA, Paxton R, Powell SM, Goodwin GW, Kuntz MJ, Han AC. | title = Regulation of branched-chain alpha-ketoacid dehydrogenase complex by covalent modification. | journal = Adv Enzyme Regul.| volume = 25| pages = 219–237 | year = 1986 | pmid = 3028049 | doi=10.1016/0065-2571(86)90016-6}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Namba Y, Yoshizawa K, Ejima A, Hayashi T, Kaneda T. | title = Coenzyme A- and nicotinamide adenine dinucleotide-dependent branched chain alpha-keto acid dehydrogenase. I. Purification and properties of the enzyme from Bacillus subtilis. | journal = J Biol Chem.| volume = 244| issue = 16| pages = 4437–4447 | year = 1969 | pmid = 4308861}}</ref> 在細菌中，這種酶參與的支鏈、長鏈脂肪酸的合成；<ref>{{cite journal | author = Lennarz WJ, ''et al.'' | title = The role of isoleucine in the biosynthesis of branched-chain fatty acids by micrococcus lysodeikticus.| journal = Biochemical and Biophysical Research Communications| volume = 6| issue = 2| pages = 1112–116| year = 1961 | pmid = 14463994 | doi = 10.1016/0006-291X(61)90395-3}}</ref>在植物中，這種酶是參與合成支鏈、長鏈的[[烴|烴]]。

BCKDC催化的分解代謝之全反應示於'''圖1'''。

==結構==
BCKDC的酶催化機制很大程度上取決於這個大型酶複合體的精細結構。這種酶複合物是由三個催化次單元組成: α-酮酸脫氫酶(alpha-ketoacid dehydrogenase)'''（E<sub>1</sub>部分）'''，[[二氫硫辛酸轉乙醯基酶|二氫硫辛酸轉乙醯基酶]](dihydrolipoyl transacylase) '''（E<sub>2</sub>部分）'''，和[[二氫硫辛醯胺脫氫酶|二氫硫辛醯胺脫氫酶]](dihydrolipoamide dehydrogenase)'''（E<sub>3</sub>部分）'''。在人體中的BCKDC核心中，有24個E<sub>2</sub>部分以八面體對稱排列。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Aevarsson A, Chuang JL, Wynn RM, Turley S, Chuang DT, Hol WGJ. | title = Crystal structure of human branched-chain α-ketoacid dehydrogenase and the molecular basis of multienzyme complex deficiency in maple syrup urine disease| journal = Structure| volume = 8| issue = 3| pages = 277–291| year = 2000 | pmid = 10745006| doi = 10.1016/S0969-2126(00)00105-2}}</ref>24 E<sub>2</sub>次單元聚合物分兩部分，12個E<sub>1</sub>α2β2四聚體和6個E<sub>3</sub>同二聚體以非共價方式結合。除了E<sub>1</sub>/E<sub>3</sub>-結合區域，在E<sub>2</sub>次單元上，有2個其他重要的結構區域：

（i）以該蛋白質的氨基末端部分的硫辛醯-軸承結構域(lipoyl-bearing domain)

（ii）在蛋白質羧基端的內核區域(inner-core domain)。

[[File:Swinging_arm_of_BCKDC.png|thumb]]
內核區域是由兩個區間片段（連接子）連接到E<sub>2</sub>次單元的其他兩個區域。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Chuang DT. | title = Molecular studies of mammalian branched-chain alpha-keto acid dehydrogenase complexes: domain structures, expression, and inborn errors.| url = https://archive.org/details/sim_annals-of-the-new-york-academy-of-sciences_1989_573/page/137 | journal = Annals of the New York Academy of Sciences| volume = 573| pages = 137–154| year = 1989 | pmid = 2699394 | doi=10.1111/j.1749-6632.1989.tb14992.x}}</ref>內核區域對形成酶複合物的低聚核(oligomeric core)和催化醯基轉移酶的反應是必須的（由“機制”一節中所示）。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Chuang DT, Hu CW, Ku LS, Markovitz PJ, Cox RP. | title = Subunit structure of the dihydrolipoyl transacylase component of branched-chain alpha-keto acid dehydrogenase complex from bovine liver. Characterization of the inner transacylase core. | journal = J Biol Chem| volume = 260| issue = 25| pages = 13779–86| year = 1985 | pmid = 4055756}}</ref> E<sub>2</sub>的硫辛醯區域可藉由上述提到連結子的彈性構像，使其在組裝好的BCKDC上之E<sub>1</sub>、E<sub>2</sub>和E<sub>3</sub>次單元的活性區位間自由擺動。（參照'''圖2'''）<ref>{{cite journal | author = Reed LJ, Hackert ML. | title = Structure-function relationships in dihydrolipoamide acyltransferases. | journal = J Biol Chem| volume = 265| issue = 16| pages = 8971–8974| year = 1990 | pmid = 2188967}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Perham RN. | title = Domains, motifs, and linkers in 2-oxo acid dehydrogenase multienzyme complexes: a paradigm in the design of a multifunctional protein. | journal = Biochemistry| volume = 30| issue = 35| pages = 8501–8512| year = 1991 | pmid = 1888719 | doi = 10.1021/bi00099a001}}</ref>因此就功能及結構方面來說，E<sub>2</sub>部分在BCKDC催化的整個反應扮演著重要的角色。

每個子單元的作用如下

===E<sub>1</sub>次單元===
E<sub>1</sub>採用[[硫胺素焦磷酸|硫胺素焦磷酸]]（TPP）作為催化的輔助因子。 E<sub>1</sub>催化α-酮酸的脫羧反應和後來的硫辛醯結構部分，以共價結合於E<sub>2</sub>次單元的還原反應（另一催化輔因子）。

===E<sub>2</sub>次單元===
E<sub>2</sub>催化醯基(acyl group)從硫辛醯部分轉至的輔酶A（化學計量的輔因子，stoichiometric cofactor）。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Heffelfinger SC, Sewell ET, Danner DJ. | title = Identification of specific subunits of highly purified bovine liver branched-chain ketoacid dehydrogenase. | journal = Biochemistry| volume = 22| issue = 24| pages = 5519–5522| year = 1983 | pmid = 6652074 | doi = 10.1021/bi00293a011}}</ref>

===E<sub>3</sub>次單元===

在E3<sub>3</sub>部分是[[黃素蛋白|黃素蛋白]](flavoprotein)，且其可作為氧化劑並利用FAD（催化輔因子）重新氧化還原E<sub>2</sub>次單元上的硫辛醯硫部分(lipoyl sulfur residues)；然後FAD將這些質子和電子轉移到NAD+（化學計量的輔因子，stoichiometric cofactor）以完成反應循環。

